      "name": "In-scope domain: FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry, blood analog fluids",
      "description": "The CFD model is applicable only to the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump geometry at rotational speeds between 2500 and 3500 RPM and flow rates between 3 and 7 L/min. Blood analog fluids with hematocrit 35–45% are in scope. Extrapolation to other pump geometries or operating regimes is explicitly excluded."
    },
